org.interledger.psk

インタフェース PskMessage


  • public interface PskMessage
    This interface represents the message format as defined in the Pre-Shared Key Transport Protocol.

    • ネストされたクラスのサマリー

    • メソッドの詳細

      • builder

        static PskMessage.Builder builder()
        Get the default builder.
        戻り値:
        a PskMessage.Builder instance.

      • getPublicHeaders

        List<PskMessage.Header> getPublicHeaders()
        Returns a list of all public headers in the message. Note that all parties may view the public headers.
        戻り値:
        all of the public headers, or an empty list.

      • getPublicHeaders

        List<PskMessage.Header> getPublicHeaders(String headerName)
        Returns the all the public headers with the specified name.
        パラメータ:
        headerName - The name of the header(s) to return
        戻り値:
        the public headers whose name matches the parameter, or an empty list.

      • getPrivateHeaders

        List<PskMessage.Header> getPrivateHeaders()
        Returns a list of all private headers in the message, provided that either the message was not encrypted, or the private portion of the message has been decrypted by the receiver.
        戻り値:
        the private headers or an empty list.

      • getPrivateHeaders

        List<PskMessage.Header> getPrivateHeaders(String headerName)
        Returns a list of all private headers in the message with the specified name. Note that this depends on either the message not being encrypted, or that the private portion of the message has already been decrypted by the receiver.
        パラメータ:
        headerName - The name of the header(s) to return
        戻り値:
        the private headers whose name matches the parameter, or an empty list.

      • getEncryptionHeader

        PskEncryptionHeader getEncryptionHeader()
        Get the encryption header.
        戻り値:
        the type of encryption used

      • getNonceHeader

        PskNonceHeader getNonceHeader()
        Get the nonce header.
        戻り値:
        the nonce header (or null if no nonce header is set)

      • getData

        byte[] getData()
        Returns the application data included in the private portion of the message, provided that either the message is not encrypted, or has already been decrypted by the receiver.
        戻り値:
        a byte[] data
